output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. CMF Number: - Present: CMF:11240015, indicating this is electoral propaganda
2. Candidate Reference: - Mentions "Lasconi" who is a presidential candidate (ELENA-VALERICA LASCONI) - Also mentions "Stancu" and references USR - References both parliamentary and presidential candidates
3. Wide Population Address: - Clearly addresses the general public - Uses paid advertising with significant reach (40,000-45,000 impressions) - Uses broad call to action "Votați USR!"
4. Electoral Objective: - Clear electoral objective with direct call to vote ("Votați USR!") - Presents a political message against "clanuri" and for "schimbarea sistemului"
5. Journalism vs Propaganda: - This is clearly campaign material, not journalism - Contains campaign slogans and direct calls to action
6. Personal Opinion: - Not a personal opinion but an official party communication (has CMF number) - Published by USR officially (as per byline)
The post mixes parliamentary election messaging (which is still allowed) with presidential candidate messaging (Lasconi) after the propaganda period has ended for presidential elections.

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This post constitutes electoral propaganda because: - Contains official campaign elements (CMF number) - Makes direct reference to presidential candidate Lasconi - Contains explicit call to vote - Is a paid advertisement with significant reach - Mixes parliamentary and presidential messaging
conclusion.message-for-police: Uniunea Salvați România (USR), pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin continuarea propagandei electorale pentru candidatul prezidențial Elena Lasconi după încheierea perioadei legale de campanie, prin intermediul unei postări sponsorizate pe Facebook (ID: 1075626137371290). Postarea, difuzată după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024, conține referințe directe la candidatul prezidențial și îndemnuri explicite la vot, având un impact semnificativ demonstrat prin reach-ul de peste 40,000 de impresii. Materialul este în mod clar propagandă electorală, având număr CMF (11240015) și fiind plătit de partidul USR.
